var book = {
	"name": "KWABASEROMA",
	"numChapters": 16,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kubhala mna Pawulos, umkhonzi kaYesu *Krestu, *umthunywa owabizwayo, wamiselwa ukuvakalisa iindaba ezimnandi zikaThixo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ezi ndaba uThixo wathembisa ngazo kwangaphambili *ngabashumayeli bakhe *eziBhalweni eziNgcwele.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ezi ndaba ke zibhekiselele kuNyana wakhe, owazalwa engowomlibo kaDavide ngokobuntu,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> waza ngamandla oMoya oyiNgcwele wabonakaliswa ngesiganeko sokuvuka kwabafileyo ukuba unguNyana kaThixo. Lo Nyana kaThixo nguYesu iNkosi yethu;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> endathi ngaye ndenzelwa isisa sokuba ngumthunywa ngenxa yakhe, ukuze ndikhokelele izizwe zonke ekukholweni nasekumthobeleni;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> eniphakathi kwazo nani, nina babiziweyo bakaYesu Krestu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kuni nonke, bathandwa bakaThixo abaseRoma, nina nibiziweyo naba ngabakaThixo, ndithi: Makube lubabalo noxolo oluvela kuThixo uBawo wethu, neNkosi uYesu Krestu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kuqala ke, ndiyambulela uThixo wam ngoYesu Krestu ngenxa yenu nonke, kuba ukholo lwenu ludumile kulo lonke ihlabathi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kaloku uThixo endimkhonzayo ngomxhelo wam ngokushumayela iindaba ezimnandi zoNyana wakhe, uyandingqinela ukuba ndihlala ndinikhumbula.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ndiyakhunga emithandazweni yam, ukuba uThixo angáde ngokwentando yakhe andiphumelelise ukunihambela.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kaloku ndilangazelela ukunibona, ukuze ndinabele siphiwo sithile kwezoMoya, ukuze nomelezeke.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ndithetha ukuthi nina kunye nam sivuseleleke: nina ngokholo lwam, nam ke ngokholo lwenu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngoko ke, mawethu, ndifuna ukuba niyiqonde into yokuba kudala ndazimisela ukunihambela, kodwa ndaba soloko ndithintelwa kwada kwanamhla. Bendifuna ziqhamo zithile zeendaba ezimnandi naphakathi kwenu, kwanjengaphakathi kwezinye iintlanga.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kaloku ndimelwe kukushumayela kubo bonke: kwabaphucukileyo nakwabangaphucukanga, kwizilumko nakwabangaziyo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngenxa yoko ke ndingxamele ukuzishumayela iindaba ezimnandi nakuni baseRoma.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Andinazintloni ngazo iindaba ezimnandi zikaKrestu. Zingamandla kaThixo okusindisa bonke abakholwayo, umJuda kuqala, kwanowolunye uhlanga ngokunjalo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ngezi ndaba zimnandi kaloku kutyhilwa indlela uThixo asenza amalungisa ngayo: kungokholo qha, njengoko zitshoyo neziBhalo ukuthi: “Ngokholo lwakhe olilungisa uya kudla ubomi.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ingqumbo kaThixo ibonakala ivela ezulwini. Yona ichasene naso sonke isono nokungalungisi kwabantu abayithintelayo inyaniso ngokona.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Unobangela wale ngqumbo kukuba oko kunokwaziwa ngoThixo kucacile kubo, kuba uThixo wakubonakalisa kubo ngokwakhe.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kaloku imo engabonwayo kaThixo – ndithetha amandla akhe angapheliyo kwanobuThixo bakhe – ibonakala kakuhle kwasekudalweni kwehlabathi. Kaloku iqondakala ngezinto azenzileyo uThixo. Ngenxa yoko abantu abanasiphephelo mpela.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bayamazi uThixo, kodwa abamdumisi ngokumfaneleyo, abambuleli nokumbulela. Basuke baba ngabacinga izinto ezingento, yaza ingqiqo yabo yamfiliba.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bazicingela ukuba bazizilumko, ukanti baziziyatha.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bashiye ubuqaqawuli bukaThixo ongafiyo, baya kukhonza umfanekiso womntu ofayo, noweentaka, nowezilo ezizitho zine, nowezilo ezirhubuluzayo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kungoko athe uThixo, ngenxa yeminqweno yeentliziyo zabo, wabanikela kwiintlondi zabo, ukuba bahlazisane ngemizimba yabo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Aba bantu ke bagqwethe inyaniso kaThixo ngobuxoki. Bahlonela isidalwa, basikhonze, baze bamlibale uMdali, yena ongowokubongwa ngonaphakade. *Amen.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngenxa yoko ke, uThixo ubanikele ezinkanukweni ezilihlazo. Ewe, nditsho namabhinqa la abo ayalalana ngokuchasene nendalo yemizimba yawo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kwangokunjalo namadoda akuyekile ukulala namabhinqa, aza atshiswa kukukhanukana. Amadoda enza amanyala kwamanye amadoda, aze ke afumane isohlwayo esiwafaneleyo, esiyimbuyekezo yokulahleka kwawo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ekubeni ke bengakukhathalelanga ukuhlala bemazi uThixo, yena wabayekela kwezo ngcinga zabo zingcolileyo, baza benza izinto ezingafanelekanga.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bagqithisile ukukhohlakala nokona, ukubawa nokwenza ububi. Bazele ngumona nobugebenga, luchuku nenkohliso nentiyo. Bayahleba,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bayangcikivana, bamthiyile uThixo, bathanda ukulwa, banekratshi, bayaqhayisa, benza ububi, ababathobeli abazali.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Abanangqondo, abathembeki, abanabubele, abananceba.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bayawazi ummiselo kaThixo wokuba abo bazenzayo izinto ezinjalo bafanelwe kukufa; kodwa abaneli nje kukuzenza ezi zinto, koko basuka babakhuthaze nabo bazenzayo."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Nakuwe ke mntundini ugwebayo, nokuba ungubani, amatyholo aphelile. Ewe, ngokugweba omnye, uzigweba ngokwakho. Kaloku wena ugwebayo, wenza kwaezo zinto ugweba omnye ngazo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Siyazi ke ukuba uThixo ubagweba ngokufanelekileyo abo benza izinto ezingalunganga.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Wena kanye, mntundini ubagwebayo abo bazenzayo izinto ezinjalo, wenza kwaezo zinto. Uba ke wena uThixo akayi kukugweba na?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Okanye ubudelile ububele bakhe obukhulu, nokunyamezela kwakhe, nokuza kade komsindo wakhe? Akwazi na ukuba bububele bukaThixo obukusa enguqukweni?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngenxa yokuba unentliziyo elukhuni, ungaguquki, uzibizela ingqumbo ngemini yengqumbo. Ngaloo mini iya kucaca indlela agweba ngayo uThixo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngaloo mini uThixo uya kuvuza elowo nalowo ngokwemisebenzi yakhe.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> UThixo ubavuza ngobomi obungonaphakade abo banomonde ekwenzeni imisebenzi emihle, belangazelela isidima newonga nokungafi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kanti ke uza ngomsindo nengqumbo kwabo banenkani, bayityeshelayo inyaniso ngokungalungisi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kuya kubakho imbandezelo nobunzima kubantu bonke abenza okubi, kumJuda kuqala kwanakowolunye uhlanga ngokunjalo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kuya kubakho isidima newonga noxolo kubantu bonke abenza okulungileyo, kumJuda kuqala kwanakowolunye uhlanga ngokunjalo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kaloku uThixo akanamkhethe.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bonke abonileyo bengekho phantsi *komthetho kaMosis, baya kutshabalala bengaphandle kwawo; nabo bonke abonileyo bephantsi komthetho kaMosis, baya kugwetywa ngawo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kaloku abantu abalungileyo ngokukaThixo asingabo abo bawuva nje umthetho bangayenzi into oyithethayo. Ngabo bayenzayo into eyalelwa ngumthetho abangamalungisa.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Abantu abangengomaJuda àbanawo umthetho kaMosis; kodwa xa bathe ngokwemvelo bahamba ngokomthetho, bangumthetho ngokwabo, nangona bengenawo umthetho kaMosis.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ukuziphatha kwabo kubonakalisa ukuba ngemvelo bayakwazi okusemthethweni. Nezazela zabo ziyakungqina oku, kuba ngamanye amaxa ziyabagweba, zize ngawambi zibagwebele.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngokweendaba ezimnandi endizishumayelayo kuya kuba njalo mhla uThixo aya kuzigweba ngoYesu Krestu nezinto abazifihlayo abantu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Uyabona wena unegama lobuJuda, wayame *ngomthetho kaMosis; uqhayisa ngoThixo;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> uyayazi intando kaThixo; ukhonjiswe okulungileyo ngumthetho.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kananjalo wena ukholose ngokuthi ungumkhokeli weemfama, ulukhanyiso lwâbo basebumnyameni,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> umkhokeli weziyatha, umfundisi weentsana, kuba unawo umthetho ofumbethe ulwazi nenyaniso.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ndithi wena ke umfundisayo omnye, akuzifundisi ngani wena? Wena uthi makungebiwa, ubelani?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Wena uthi makungakrexezwa, ukrexezelani? Wena ukruqukileyo zizithixo, ubelani ezindlwini zonqulo?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Wena ke uziqhayisayo ngokuba unomthetho, umhlaziselani uThixo ngokuwaphula umthetho?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Kuba igama likaThixo linyeliswa ngenxa yenu phakathi kweentlanga,” njengoko zitshoyo *iziBhalo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ulwaluko luyanceda okunene ukuba uyawugcina umthetho kaMosis. Kodwa ukuba uyawaphula umthetho, ulwaluko lusuka lufane nokungaluki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ukuba umntu ongalukanga uyayigcina imimiselo yomthetho, uThixo uya kuthi ukungaluki kwakhe kukwaluka.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Nina maJuda, nangona nalukileyo, ninawo umthetho eziBhalweni, nibe noko ningawenzi, niya kugwetywa ziintlanga ezithe zingalukanga nje zawugcina umthetho.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> UmJuda asingomJuda ngokwangaphandle, nolwaluko asilulo olo lwangaphandle enyameni.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> UmJuda ngulowo ungumJuda ngokwangaphakathi, nolwaluko lolwentliziyo ngoMoya kaThixo, kungabi ngammiselo nje. Umntu onjalo ke ukholekile kuThixo, nangona angànconywayo ngabantu."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ungcono ngani na ke umJuda? Lunceda ntoni ke lona ulwaluko lwakhe?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Lulunge kakhulu, ngeendlela zonke. Okokuqala uThixo ugcinise udaba lwakhe kuwo amaJuda.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kuya kuthini ke ukuba athile kuwo akakholwanga? Ngaba uThixo uya kuthi ngokungathembeki kwawo angathembeki naye?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nakanye! UThixo yena uhlala enyanisekile, nangona bangade bonke abantu babe ngamaxoki, njengoko *iziBhalo zitshoyo ukuthi: “Umelwe kukubonakala ngamazwi akho ukuba uthembekile, woyise ekuthethweni kwetyala lakho.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Xa ukungalungisi kwethu kucacisa ukulungisa kukaThixo, siya kuthini ke? Ngaba sinokuthi akalungisi uThixo xa abonakalisa umsindo wakhe, ngabula thina bantu?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nakanye! Ukuba ebengelolungisa uThixo, ebengaligweba njani ihlabathi?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ukuba ke ngokuxoka kwam inyaniso kaThixo idandalaza ngakumbi ukuze sicace isidima sakhe, ndisagwetyelwani na ke ngokomoni?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Yini na ke ukuba singabi sesisithi: “Masenze okubi, ukuze kuvele okulungileyo”? Kakade abathile bandinyelisa besithi nditsho! Abo batshoyo baya kugwetywa ngokubafaneleyo!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ke, ngaba thina maJuda silungile na kunabanye? Hayi, nakanye! Kaloku sendiwatyholile amaJuda kwanabezinye iintlanga ndisithi basesonweni bebonke,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> njengoko iziBhalo zitshoyo ukuthi: “Akukho namnye ulilungisa;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> akukho mntu uqondayo; akukho umfunayo uThixo!",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bonke bamfulathele; akukho yabo xa bebonke. Akukho wenza okulungileyo; hayi namnye!",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Yinto ebolileyo intetho yabo; ngeelwimi zabo bahlala bekhohlisa. Amazwi emilebe yabo abubuhlungu benyoka;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> umlomo wabo uzele zizishwabulo ezikrakra.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bakungxamele ukuphalaza igazi;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> yimbuqe nosizi emkhondweni wabo;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> yona indlela yoxolo abayazanga;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ewe, abamoyiki konke uThixo.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Siyazi ke ukuba konke okuthethwa ngumthetho, kuwiselwa abaphantsi komthetho; ukuze bonke basikwe umlomo, nehlabathi lonke lifumaneke linetyala kuThixo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kaloku akukho mntu uya kuba lilungisa kuThixo ngakugcina kwakhe umthetho; into eyenziwa ngumthetho kukwazisa abantu ngesono.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngoku ke indlela uThixo abalungisa ngayo abantu ibonakalisiwe, ingeyiyo eyomthetho. Kambe ke iyangqinelwa *ngumthetho kaMosis *nangabashumayeli bamandulo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Yona kukukholwa nokuzinikela kuYesu Krestu. UThixo ubenza amalungisa bonke abakholwayo kuYesu, kuba akanamkhethe.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kaloku bonke bonile; bayalabalaba kubuqaqawuli ababulungiselelwe nguThixo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kanti ke uThixo uyabababala abantu; ubenzela isisa: nangona bengafanelanga ubagwebela ngaye uYesu Krestu obakhululayo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> UThixo wammisela uYesu ukuba abe lidini lokungxengxezela izono zabakholwayo. Ukufa kwakhe yindlela uThixo abenza ngayo amalungisa abantu. Kumaxesha adlulileyo uThixo wazibamba akabagweba aboni;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> kodwa ke namhlanje akasayenzi loo nto – ngoku walatha indlela abenza ngayo amalungisa. Ngale ndlela ke uThixo utyhila ubulungisa bakhe, emenza abe lilungisa wonke okholwayo kuYesu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kukho nto singaziqhayisa ngayo ke? Hayi, ayikho. Ngasizathu sini na? Kuba sigcina umthetho kaMosis? Hayi, ngenxa yokuba sikholwa.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kuba kaloku sigqibe kwelithi uThixo wenza abantu babe ngamalungisa ngokholo, kungengakuthobela kwabo umthetho.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kanene uThixo ungowamaJuda odwa na? Akanguye na owezizwe nazo? Ewe, ngowazo nazo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kaloku uThixo mnye kuphela; ugwebela amaJuda ngokukholwa kwawo, nezizwe azigwebele ngokukholwa kwazo ngokunjalo.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ngaba ke siyawutshitshisa umthetho kaMosis ngokukholwa? Nakanye! Siyawuxhasa."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Sithini na ke ngobawo uAbraham esiyinzala yakhe?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ukuba ebenziwe ilungisa ngenxa yokufezekisa kwakhe umthetho, ebengaqhayisayo; kodwa ngoku akanandlela yakuqhayisa phambi koThixo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Zithini kanene *iziBhalo? Zithi: “UAbraham wakholwa kuThixo, waza ngenxa yoko wabalelwa ekubeni lilungisa nguThixo.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku umntu osebenzayo wamkela umvuzo oyimfanelo yakhe, ungesiso isipho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ke umntu ongathembelanga misebenzini yakhe, koko okholwa kuThixo ogwebela umoni, uba lilungisa phambi koThixo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Unoyolo ke umntu othe waba lilungisa phambi koThixo, engakusebenzelanga oko. Lolu yolo ke uDavide aluncomayo xa athi:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Hayi uyolo lwabaluxolelweyo ukreqo lwabo nguThixo, abazono zabo zingcwatyiweyo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Unoyolo lowo ithe iNkosi ayazibalela kuye izono zakhe.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngaba olu yolo lolwamaJuda kuphela? Hayi, lukwalolwazo neentlanga, kuba iziBhalo zithi: “UAbraham wakholwa kuThixo, waza ngenxa yoko wabalelwa ekubeni lilungisa nguThixo.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Waba lilungisa nini? Kwakungaphambi kokwaluka kwakhe okanye emva kwako? Kwakungaphambi kokwaluka kwakhe.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kaloku wathi engekaluki uAbraham, ekholwa kodwa, wabalelwa ekubeni lilungisa nguThixo; waza waluka emva koko. Olu lwaluko ke lwaba luphawu olusisiqinisekiso sobulungisa bakhe. Ngale ndlela ke uAbraham nguyise wabo bonke abathe bakholwa kuThixo, baza benziwa amalungisa nguye nangona bangalukanga.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ukwanguyise wabalukileyo abanganelanga kwaluka nje, kodwa abathe ngokukholwa kuThixo bahamba ekhondweni lika-Abraham, owakholwa engekaluki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> UThixo wathembisa uAbraham nenzala yakhe ukuba ihlabathi baya kulima. Esi sithembiso asenziwanga ngakuba ethe wathobela umthetho kaMosis, kodwa wathenjiswa ngenxa yokuba wakholwa, waza wabalelwa ekubeni lilungisa nguThixo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kaloku ukuba ilifa lifunyanwa kuphela ngâbo bawuthobelayo umthetho, ukukholwa koba kwenziwe into engento, nesithembiso eso singaba sitshitshisiwe.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ingqumbo kaThixo kaloku ibangwa kukwaphulwa komthetho wakhe; kodwa apho ungekhoyo umthetho akukho kwaphulwa kwamthetho.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngoko ke ilifa lifunyanwa ngokukholwa, oko kukuthi ngesisa. Ngale ndlela isithembiso simiselwe yonke inzala ka-Abraham. Le nzala ke asingabo nje abo bawugcinayo umthetho, kodwa ikwangâbo bakholwayo njengaye. Kaloku uAbraham ngubawo wethu sonke,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> njengokuba zisitsho *iziBhalo ukuthi: “Ndikwenze uyise wezizwe ezininzi.” KuThixo ke uAbraham ngubawo wethu sonke; lo Thixo uAbraham athe wakholwa kuye; lo Thixo unika abafileyo ubomi; lo Thixo uthetha ngelizwi zitsho izinto ezingekabikho zibekho.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> UAbraham wakholwa, wathemba, naxa ithemba lalingekho. Wakholwa okokuba woba “nguyise wezizwe ezininzi,” njengoko iziBhalo zitshoyo ukuthi: “Iya kuba ngako ke inzala yakho ukuba ninzi kwayo.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Wayemayela nekhulu leminyaka ezelwe, kodwa akatyhafanga elukholweni akucinga ngokwaluphala kwakhe nangobudlolo bukaSara.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hayi, akasithandabuzanga isithembiso sikaThixo ngokungakholwa; waya esomelela elukholweni, embonga uThixo,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> eqinisekile ukuba uThixo unako ukukwenza oko akuthembisileyo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kungoko “wabalelwa ekubeni lilungisa nguThixo.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> La mazwi athi “wabalelwa ekubeni lilungisa” akabhekisi kuye yedwa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hayi, abhekisa nakuthi, thina sasiza kuba ngamalungisa, thina sikholwayo kuThixo owamvusayo uYesu iNkosi yethu kwabafileyo,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> yena owanikelwa ekufeni ngenxa yezono zethu, waza wabuya wavuswa, ukuze thina sibe ngamalungisa."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Njengoko sikholwa, sígwetyelwe nguThixo, sinoxolo naye ngenxa yeNkosi yethu uYesu Krestu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kaloku sibe nako ukungena ngoKrestu ngokukholwa kolu babalo sikulo. Siyaqhayisa ke sithembe ukuba nenxaxheba ebuqaqawulini bukaThixo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngaphezu koko, siqhayisa nangeembandezelo ezi, sisazi nje ukuba iimbandezelo zisiqhelisa ukunyamezela.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ke ukunyamezela kubonisa ukuba sicikidekile. Ukucikideka ke kudala ithemba.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ithemba ke lona alidanisi, kuba uthando lukaThixo luthululelwe ezintliziyweni zethu ngoMoya oyiNgcwele esamnikwayo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kuba kaloku oko besisengama-athalala, uKrestu uthe ngexesha elimiswe nguThixo, wabafela abangamhloneliyo uThixo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Inqabile into yokuba umntu afele omnye, naxa mhlawumbi anokubhaqeka umntu onesibindi sokufela umntu olungileyo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ke yena uThixo ukuqondakalisile ukusithanda kwakhe ngokuthi uKrestu asifele sisengaboni!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sigwetyelwe nje ngenxa yegazi lakhe, kokukhona siya kusindiswa ngaye kuyo ingqumbo kaThixo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kaloku besikade siziintshaba noThixo, saxolelaniswa naye ngokufa koNyana wakhe. Kobeka phi ke ukusindiswa kwethu ngokudla kwakhe ubomi!",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngaphezu koko ke, sineqhayiya novuyo ngaye uThixo, ngenxa yeNkosi yethu uYesu Krestu, esithe ngayo saxolelaniswa noThixo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Njengoko isono sangena ehlabathini ngenxa yomntu omnye, ukufa kwangena ngaso isono. Ngokunjalo ke nokufa kwalutyhutyha lonke uluntu, kuba bonke abantu bôna.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Isono ke sabakho ehlabathini ungekabikho *umthetho kaMosis. Ke, apho kungekho mthetho, isono sokwaphula umthetho asinakubalelwa mntwini.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ke ukufa kwakutshatshele ukususela kuAdam kwada kwaya kuthi gaa kuMosis, nakwabo basono singafani nesika-Adam. Lo Adam ke wayengumfuziselo waloo Mntu wayeza kufika.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kodwa isono sika-Adam asinakulinganiswa nesisa sikaThixo. Kaloku naxa kwafa abantu abaninzi nje ngenxa yesono salowo mnye unguAdam, lona ubabalo lukaThixo esalufumana ngaloo mntu mnye unguKrestu, lwaphuphumela kubantu abaninzi ngakumbi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kanti ke isiqhamo sesipho sikaThixo asinakulinganiswa nesiphumo sesono saloo mntu. Kaloku isiphumo sesono saloo mntu saba kukugwetywa, kodwa isiqhamo sesisa sikaThixo esabakho ngenxa yezono ezininzi, saba kukukhululwa kwabantu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ukuba ukufa kwakutshatshele ngenxa yesono saloo mntu, abo balwamkelayo ubabalo oluphuphumayo kwanesipho sokwenziwa amalungisa, baya kudla ubomi ngokugqithisileyo ngaloo mntu mnye unguYesu Krestu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ngako ke, njengokuba kwathi ngasono sinye, bonke abantu bagwetywa, ngokunjalo kuya kuthi nangesenzo esinye esilungileyo, bonke abantu bagwetyelwe, badle ubomi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kuba njengokuba kwathi, ngokungeva kwalowo mnye unguAdam, abaninzi bafumaneka bengaboni, ngokunjalo kuya kuthi nangokuthobela kwalowo mnye unguKrestu, abaninzi benziwe amalungisa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ke kaloku wakungena umthetho kaMosis, isono sanda. Kodwa apho kwânda khona ukona, lwaphuphuma ngakumbi ubabalo asibabala ngalo uThixo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Njengokuba ke isono salawula ngokufa, ngokunjalo nobabalo lulawula ngokwenziwa kwethu amalungisa nguThixo. Lonu lusikhokelela ebomini obungonaphakade ngenxa kaYesu Krestu iNkosi yethu."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Síthini na ke ngoko? Síhlale sihleli esonweni ukuze ubabalo lwande?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Nakanye! Thina kaloku safa kuso isono. Singathini ke ukuba siqhubele phambili sisona?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Anazi na ukuba thina sonke sibhaptiziweyo samanywa noKrestu Yesu, sabhaptizelwa ekufeni kwakhe?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngokunjalo ngokubhaptizwa sangcwatywa kunye noKrestu. Njengokuba ke uKrestu wavuswayo kwabafileyo ngamandla obungangamsha bukaYise, nathi ngokunjalo masiphile ubomi obutsha.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kaloku xa simanywe naye ekufeni kwakhe, simanywe naye nasekuvukeni kwakhe ekufeni.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Siyazi ke ukuba isimo sethu esidala sabethelelwa emnqamlezweni noKrestu, khon' ukuze igunya lesono liphuthiswe nasemizimbeni yethu, size singabi salawulwa sisono.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kaloku umntu ofileyo ukhululekile esonweni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ukuba ke safa kunye noKrestu, siyakholwa ukuba sodla ubomi kwakunye naye.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Siyazi ke ukuba uKrestu evusiwe nje kwabafileyo, akayi kuba safa – ukufa akusayi kuba nagunya kuye.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kuba wafa kwakanye, efela isono; kodwa ngoku udla ubomi, ephilela uThixo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngokunjalo nani zibaleleni ekubeni ningabafileyo okunene kuso isono, niphilela uThixo ngobomi enibudlayo, nimanywe noKrestu Yesu, iNkosi yethu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngoko ke isono masingayilawuli imizimba yenu efayo. Sanukuzivumela iinkanuko zemizimba yenu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kananjalo imizimba yenu musani ukuyinikela esonweni, nize none ngamalungu ayo; koko zinikeleni nina ziqu kuThixo, ningabaphila bevuke ekufeni nje. Ngenxa yoko ke wanikeleni kuThixo amalungu emizimba yenu, ukuze nenze okulungileyo ngawo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Isono masinganilawuli, kuba anikho phantsi komthetho, niphantsi kobabalo lwesisa sikaThixo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Síthini na ke ngoko? Sóne na, kuba singekho phantsi kwawo umthetho, siphantsi kobabalo? Nakanye!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kakade niyazi ukuba lowo nizinikela kuye ukuba anilawule, ngokwenyani niyamkhonza, nimthobele. Abalawulwa sisono ke baba sisisulu sokufa, kodwa abamthobeleyo uThixo ubenza amalungisa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ke kaloku, makubulelwe kuThixo, kuba nanifudula nilawulwa sisono, kodwa ngoku niyithobela ngokupheleleyo imfundiso eniyifundisiweyo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nakhululwa ke kuso isono, naba phantsi kobulungisa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ngenxa yobuthathaka bemvelo yenu mandingantsonkothi. Njengoko nanizinikele ngokupheleleyo ukuba nenze ukungcola nokwaphula umthetho, nize nichasane nomthetho; ngokunjalo ke nangoku zinikeleni ngokupheleleyo ukuze nenze okulungileyo, khon' ukuze nahluke.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Okuya nanilawulwa sisono naningekho phantsi kobulungisa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ke, benizuza ntoni ngaloo nto? Andithi izinto enanizizuza zezi nineentloni ngazo ngoku, ezi zikhokelela ekufeni?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ngoku ke, nikhululwe nje esonweni, naba ngabakaThixo, ninaso isiqhamo esibubungcwele. Le nto ke ikhokelela ebomini obungunaphakade.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Isono sinomvuzo: samkelisa ukufa; ke sona isipho asibabala ngaso uThixo ngokumanywa kwethu noKrestu Yesu iNkosi yethu, bubomi obungonaphakade."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Mawethu, ndithetha nabantu abawaziyo umthetho welakowethu; niyazi ukuba umntu uphantsi kwegunya lomthetho kuphela ngeli xesha adla ubomi ngalo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kaloku umfazi owendileyo ubotshelelwe ngumthetho endodeni yakhe, eli lixa idla ubomi; kodwa ukuba ithe yafa indoda, ukhululekile kuwo umthetho ombophelela endodeni yakhe.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngoko ke, ukuba umfazi uthe waba ngowenye indoda isaphila indoda yakhe, kothiwa ungumkrexezi. Kodwa ke ukuba ithe yafa indoda yakhe, woba ukhululekile emthethweni, aze angabi ngumkrexezi ukuba uthe waba ngowenye indoda.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kukwanjalo ke nakuni, mawethu. Ngokumanywa nomzimba kaKrestu nani nafa ngokubhekiselele kumthetho kaMosis, ukuze nibe ngabomnye, ongulo Krestu ke owavuswa kwabafileyo. Le nto ke ibanga ukuba sibe nokumsebenzela uThixo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kaloku ngokuya sasisidla ubomi, ngokweyethu intando, iinkanuko ezimbi ezivuselelwa ngumthetho zazilawula emizimbeni yethu, sisebenzela ukufa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ke, ekubeni safayo nje ngokubhekiselele kwezo zinto zazisilawula, sikhululekile ngoku emthethweni. Ngenxa yoko asisakhonzi ngendlela endala yomthetho obhaliweyo, kodwa sikhonza ngendlela entsha yoMoya.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ndithini ke xa nditshoyo? Ngaba ndithi umthetho usisono? Nakanye! Kodwa ke ngendingasazanga isono ukuba ubungekho umthetho. Kaloku nenkanuko ngendingayazanga ukuba umthetho ubungatshongo ukuthi: “Uze unganqweneli...”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Isono ke sizuze ikroba ngawo lo mthetho, sandivusela yonke inkanuko. Kaloku xa kungekho mthetho, isono sifile.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mna ke bendifudula ndiphila ungekho umthetho. Uthe ke wakufika umthetho, savuka isono,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ndafa ke mna; waza umthetho owawumiselwe ukuzisa ubomi, wafumaneka inguwona undisa ekufeni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kuba kaloku isono sizuze ikroba ngawo lo mthetho, sandilukuhla, sandibulala ngawo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Okunene umthetho ungcwele; nomyalelo ungcwele, unobulungisa, ulungile.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Umthetho ulungile nje, ungaba kukufa kum? Nakanye! Sisono esaba kukufa kum. Sona sisebenzise into elungileyo ukundizisela ukufa, saza ke sacaca into esiyiyo, khon' ukuze ngomthetho isono sibonakale sisisono ngakumbi nangakumbi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Siyazi ke ukuba umthetho ngowoMoya kaThixo, kodwa mna ndiyinyama negazi; ndiphantsi kwegunya lesono.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Into endiyenzayo yinkohla kum, kuba kaloku into endithanda ukuyenza andiyenzi, ukanti ndiyayenza endiyithiyileyo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Xa ke ndisenza into endiyithiyileyo, kucacile ukuba ndiyavuma ukuthi umthetho ulungile.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ngoko ke ayisendim owenza loo nto ndingayithandiyo, koko sisono esihleli kum esenza loo nto.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ndiyazi ukuba akuhlali nto ilungileyo kum – nditsho kwisimo sam esonakeleyo – kuba kaloku umnqweno wokwenza into elungileyo ukho kum, kodwa ukwenza andinako.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Into elungileyo endithanda ukuyenza, andiyenzi; kodwa into embi endingathandi kuyenza, ndiyayenza.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ukuba ke ndenza loo nto ndingayithandiyo, ayisendim oyenzayo, koko sisono esi sihleli kum esiyenzayo loo nto.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kambe ke ndibhaqa le nto apha kum: Kuthi xa ndifuna ukwenza into elungileyo, ndisuke ndonganyelwe kukwenza ububi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ndiyawulangazelela umthetho kaThixo ngentliziyo,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> kodwa ndibhaqa nto yimbi kwalapha kum echasene nomthetho endiwaziyo entliziyweni yam, nto leyo indithimbela esonweni esihleli kum.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hayi usizana endilulo! Ngubani na oya kundihlangula kulo mzimba usisisulu sokufa?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ndiyambulela uThixo ngoYesu Krestu iNkosi yethu! Nantsi ke imeko endikuyo: Ngokuphathelele kwendikwaziyo entliziyweni yam, okunene ndikhonza uThixo; kodwa ngokwesimo sam esonakeleyo, ndikhonza isono."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngoko ke àbagwetywa abo bamanywe noKrestu Yesu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kaloku ngokumanywa kwam noKrestu Yesu, uMoya umniki-bomi undikhulule ekulawulweni sisono nakukufa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ke wona umthetho wawungenako ukusikhulula, ngenxa yokonakala kwesimo sethu. Kodwa yena uThixo wamthumela uNyana wakhe, ekwisimo esifana nesimo sethu esonakeleyo, waza wasigweba isono emntwini wenyama negazi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Le nto uThixo uyenzele ukuze injongo yomthetho izalisekiswe kuthi, thina singaphiliyo ngokwesimo esonakeleyo, koko siphila ngokoMoya.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Abo besimo esonakeleyo banyamekela izinto zeso simo; ibe ke abo boMoya banyamekela izinto zoMoya.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ke ukunyamekela izinto zesimo esonakeleyo kusa ekufeni, kanti ke ukunyamekela ezoMoya kusa ebomini naseluxolweni.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Abo banyamekela izinto zesimo esonakeleyo baziintshaba zikaThixo, kuba kaloku abawuthobeli umthetho wakhe. Kakade abanako ukuyenza loo nto.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ábenjenjalo ke àbanako ukumkholisa uThixo konke-konke.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ke nina aningabo abaphila ngokwesimo esonakeleyo, ningabo bakhokelwa nguMoya, ukuba kambe uMoya kaThixo uhleli kuni. Ke umntu ongenaye uMoya kaKrestu akangokaKrestu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ukuba uKrestu ukho kuni, nangona umzimba ufile ngenxa yesono, uMoya yena uninika ubomi. Kaloku nenziwe amalungisa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ukuba ke uMoya kaThixo owamvusayo uYesu ekufeni ukho kuni, neyenu imizimba uThixo uya kuyinika ubomi ngoMoya wakhe okhoyo kuni.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngoko ke, mawethu, masingakholisi isimo sethu esonakeleyo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kuba xa niphila ngokweso simo, niya ekufeni; kodwa ukuba niyazitshitshisa ngamandla oMoya izenzo ezibi zomzimba, niya kudla ubomi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kaloku abo bakhokelwa nguMoya kaThixo, bangoonyana bakaThixo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> UMoya enimamkeleyo akanenzi amakhoboka, wona aphakuzelayo. Kaloku namkele uMoya onenza oonyana abathi: “Tata!” kuThixo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> UMoya ngokwakhe ungqinelana nathi ukuthi singabantwana bakaThixo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ukuba ke singabantwana bakaThixo, sikwaziindlalifa zikaThixo. Ewe, siziindlalifa kunye noKrestu, kuba kaloku siva ubunzima kunye naye, siphinde siwongwe kwakunye naye.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ndigqiba kwelithi ezi ntlungu zangoku azinakufaniswa nobuncwane esiza kubuxhamla;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> kuba indalo iphela ilangazelela ukuba uThixo ade abaveze oonyana bakhe.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kaloku indalo yathotyelwa kwimeko ephuthileyo, kungengakuthanda kwayo, kodwa kungokuthanda kwalowo wayithobayo. Phofu likho ithemba lokuba",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> nendalo ngokwayo iya kude ikhululwe kwiimbophelelo zokonakala, ize nayo isiwe enkululekweni nasebuqaqawulini babantwana bakaThixo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kuba kaloku siyazi ukuba kude kube ngokunje yonke indalo iyancwina inenimba.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Asiyiyo yodwa ke: nathi thina siphiwe uMoya osisiqinisekiso sokukhululwa kwethu nguThixo, siyancwina, silindele ukubekwa ewongeni lokuba ngoonyana bakaThixo. Yinkululeko yethu ke leyo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Okunene naxa sisindisiwe nje, sisesethembeni. Ukuba ke siyayibona into esithembe ukuyifumana, asilothemba elo. Kaloku akukho mntu uthemba ukufumana into aseleyifumene.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kodwa ke into esingayiboniyo, esithembe ukuyifumana, siyilindela ngomonde.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngokukwanjalo noMoya uyasixhasa ekusweleni kwethu amandla, kuba kaloku asiyazi eyona ndlela singathandaza ngayo. Kodwa ke kweso singqala sethu sikhohliwe uMoya ngokwakhe uyasithethelela.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ke uThixo oziphengululayo iintliziyo uyazazi iingcamango zoMoya, kuba kaloku uMoya uthethelela abantu bakaThixo ngokwentando kaThixo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Siyazi ke ukuba kuyo yonke imeko uThixo ubenzela okulungileyo abo bamthandayo, ababizwe ngokwenjongo yakhe.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kaloku abo wayeselebazi kwangaphambili, wabamisela ukuba babe ngumfanekiso woNyana wakhe, ukuze uNyana wakhe abe ngowamazibulo kusapho olukhulu.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Abo ke uThixo wabamiselayo kwangaphambili, wababiza kananjalo. Abo wababizayo, wabenza amalungisa. Abo wabenza amalungisa, wabanika iwonga.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Masithini na ke ngezi zinto? Ukuba uThixo ungakuthi ngubani onokusichasa?",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Yena kaloku akambandezanga owakhe uNyana, koko usuke wamnikela ngenxa yethu sonke. Angathini ke ukungasibabali asiphe zonke ezinye izinto?",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ngubani na oya kubamangalela abanyulwa bakaThixo, inguThixo nje obagwebelayo?",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ngubani onokubagweba, ethe wafa nje uKrestu, wathi ngaphezu koko wabuya wavuka, waza waya kuhlala ewongeni kwaThixo, apho asithethelela khona?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ngubani ke onokusahlukanisa nothando lukaKrestu? Yimbandezelo na? Yinkxwaleko na? Yintshushiso na? Yindlala na? Bubuzé na? Yingozi na? Likrele na?",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kunjengoko *iziBhalo zitshoyo ukuthi: “Ngenxa yakho sisesichengeni sokubulawa; yiyo loo nto sesifana neegusha eziya kuxhelwa nje.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kanti ke, kwezi zinto zonke sisuka soyise sitshatshele ngalowo wasithandayo.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kaloku ndiqinisekile kukuba asikuko nakufa, nabomi, nazithunywa zezulu, nazilawuli, nanto zikhoyo, nanto zizayo, naziphathamandla,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> nanto ziphezulu, nanto zingaphantsi, nditsho nasiphi na isidalwa, esiya kuba nako ukusahlula nothando lukaThixo olukuye uKrestu Yesu, iNkosi yethu."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Mna ndingokaKrestu; ndithetha inyaniso, andixoki. Kwanesazela sam, silawulwa nguMoya oyiNgcwele, siyandingqinela ukuba andixoki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ndiselusizini olukhulu, ndaye ndinentlungu engapheliyo entliziyweni yam",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ngenxa yamawethu amaSirayeli. Ewe, bendingade ndinqwenele ukuba mna ngokwam ndibe ngoqalekisiweyo nguThixo esikhundleni sawo, ndide ndahlukaniswe noKrestu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> AmaSirayeli la kaloku uThixo wawenza oonyana bakhe, wabubonakalisa kuwo nobuqaqawuli bakhe. Wenza iminqophiso nawo, wawanika umthetho neyona ndlela yonqulo, wawenzela kwanezithembiso.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ayinzala *yamanyange, kwaye kuwo kwavela uKrestu ngokobuntu, yena owongamela konke, ongulo Thixo omakadunyiswe ngonaphakade. *Amen.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Le nto ke ayithethi kuthi ilizwi likaThixo lona ngokwalo litshitshile. Asingabo bonke kaloku abaphuma kuSirayeli abangamaSirayeli ncam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kananjalo asingabo bonke abazelwe nguAbraham abayinzala yakhe ncakasana. Kaloku uThixo wathi kuAbraham: “Inzala yakho ncam iya kuphuma kunyana wakho uIsake.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Loo nto ithetha ukuthi asingabo bonke abantwana abazeleyo uAbraham abangabantwana bakaThixo. Hayi, ngabantwana besithembiso kuphela ababalelwa ekubeni bayinzala ncam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kaloku isithembiso sênziwa nguThixo ngala mazwi athi: “Ngexesha elifanelekileyo ndiya kukuvelela, waye ke uSara uya kuzala unyana.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ukuqhubela phambili mandithi: Uyise wamawele kaRabheka wayemnye, inguIsake ubawo wethu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kwathi abantwana bengekazalwa, bengekenzi nto, nokuba yelungileyo, nokuba yembi, uThixo wathi kuRabheka: “Omdala uya kuba ngumkhonzi womncinci.” Kaloku unyulo lukaThixo lusekelwe kubizo lwakhe, kungekuko nakuyiphi na into eyenziwa ngumntu;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> njengoko *iziBhalo zitshoyo ukuthi: “Ndamthanda uYakobi, ndamthiya yena uEsawu.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Síthini ke ngoko? Ngaba sinokuthi uThixo akanabulungisa? Nakanye!",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kaloku wathi kuMosis: “Ndiya kuba nenceba kulowo ndinenceba kuye, ndibe netarhu kulowo ndinetarhu kuye.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ke ukunyulwa komntu akuxhomekekanga ekuzithandeleni komntu, okanye ekwenzeni kwakhe, koko kuxhomekeke kwinceba kaThixo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kaloku iziBhalo zithi kukumkani waseJiputa: “Ndakuphakamisa ukuze ndiwabonakalise ngawe amandla am, ize negama lam lidume, linwenwe kulo lonke ihlabathi.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ngoko ke uThixo unenceba kulowo athanda ukumenzela inceba, aze ayenze lukhuni intliziyo yalowo athanda ukuyenza lukhuni.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Omnye kuni usenokuthi kum: “Ukuba ke kunjalo angathini na uThixo ukumsola umntu; kungekho bani nje unokumelana nentando kaThixo?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Mntundini, kuxa ungubani wena ukuba ungade uphendulane noThixo? Into ebunjiweyo ingátsho njani kumbumbi wayo ukuthi: “Yini na ukuba undenjenje ukundibumba?”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Akanalo kakade umbumbi ilungelo lokuthi ngamdongwe mnye enze ingqayi exabisekileyo kwanengaxabisekanga?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kukwanjalo ke nangokubhekiselele kwizinto ezenziwe nguThixo. Kaloku wayefuna ukubonakalisa ingqumbo yakhe nokwazisa ubungangamsha bakhe. Ngoko ke wabanyamezela ngomonde abo wayebaqumbele, ababemelwe kukutshatyalaliswa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Wayefuna nokubonakalisa ubuhle besihomo nesithozela sakhe kwabo abenzela inceba, abo abenza bafanele ukuthiwa jize ngewonga.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Síthí ke abo uThixo wababizayo, singemaJuda kuphela, sikwakunye nabezinye iintlanga ngokunjalo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Uthetha kwaloo nto kwiNcwadi kaHosiya, xa athi: “Abangengobantu bam ndiya kuthi bangabantu bam; nohlanga ebendingaluthandi ndiya kuthi luyintanda kum.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ewe, nakuloo ndawo kanye kwakusithiwa kubo: ‘Aningobantu bam nina;’ khona apho kanye kuya kuthiwa kubo: ‘Ningoonyana bakaThixo ophilayo.’”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ke noIsaya udanduluka athi malunga namaSirayeli: “Nangona inani loonyana bakaSirayeli lingangentlabathi yaselwandle, bambalwa kodwa kubo abaya kusindiswa,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> kuba iNkosi iya kusiwisa kamsinya isigwebo sayo ehlabathini.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kukwanjengokuba uIsaya wayetshilo ngaphambili ukuthi: “Ukuba iNkosi uSomandla ibingasishiyelanga hlumela, ngesisuke saba njengeSodom, safana neGomora.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Síthini ke ngoko? Síthi izizwe ezazingenzi migudu yakuba ngamalungisa kuThixo, zakufumana nazo ukuba ngamalungisa, zisenziwa amalungisa ngokholo.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kodwa wona amaSirayeli, nangona ayesenza imigudu yokuba ngamalungisa ngokugcina umthetho, akaphumelelanga.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ngani na? Ngenxa yokuba imigudu yawo ingasekelwanga lukholweni, kodwa isekelwe ekuzenzeleni ngokwawo. Akhubeka “elityeni elikhubekisayo,”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> eli *iziBhalo zitshoyo ngalo ukuthi: “Uyabona, ndibeka *eZiyon ilitye elikhubekisayo, ulwalwa olusisikhubekiso; lowo ukholwayo kuye akayi kudaniswa.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Mawethu, ndilangazelela ngayo yonke intliziyo yam ukuba amaSirayeli, abantu bakowethu, asindiswe, ndaye ndihlala ndimbongoza uThixo ngenxa yawo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ndingawangqinela ukuba anenzondelelo ngezinto zikaThixo, kodwa engenalo ulwazi olululo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Akayazanga indlela uThixo abalungisa ngayo abantu, aza afuna ukuba ngamalungisa ngeyawo indlela. Ngokwenjenjalo ke akayithobelanga indlela uThixo abenza ngayo amalungisa abantu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku umthetho ufikelele esiphelweni ngoKrestu, khon' ukuze wonke umntu abe lilungisa kuba ekholwa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Malunga nokuba lilungisa phambi koThixo ngokuthobela umthetho, uMosis ubhale esithi: “Umntu owugcinayo umthetho, wophila ngawo.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kodwa malunga nokwenziwa ilungisa ngokholo kuthiwa: “Musa ukuthi entliziyweni yakho: Ngubani na oya kunyuka aye ezulwini?” (oko kukuthi ahlise uKrestu).",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Okanye musa ukuthi: Ngubani na oya kuhla aye enzonzobileni?” (oko kukuthi ukuya kunyusa uKrestu kwabafileyo).",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngaba ke kukuthini oko? Kukuthi: “Ilizwi likaThixo likufuphi kuwe, lisemlonyeni wakho nasentliziyweni yakho.” Ilizwi lokholo esilivakalisayo nali:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ukuba uthe wavuma ngomlomo ukuba uYesu yiNkosi, wakholwa nangentliziyo ukuba uThixo wamvusa kwabafileyo, wosindiswa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kaloku umntu ukholwa ngentliziyo, aze abe lilungisa phambi koThixo; uvuma ngomlomo, aze asindiswe.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> IziBhalo kaloku zithi: “Lowo ukholwayo kuye akayi kudaniswa.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ke ngoko akukho mahluko phakathi komJuda nowolunye uhlanga, kuba le Nkosi inye ikwayinkosi yabo bonke. Kaloku ibasikelela ngesisa ngendyebo yayo bonke abo bazibika kuyo,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> kuba: “Lowo uzibika ebiza igama leNkosi wosindiswa.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bangazibika njani kulowo bangàkholwayo kuye; bengakholwa njani bengevanga? Bangeva njani kungekho mntu ushumayelayo;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bengashumayela njani bengathunywanga? Kaloku iziBhalo zithi: “Ngumbono omhle ukubukela izigidimi zisihla zinyuka zihambisa iindaba ezimnandi!”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kodwa asingabo bonke abazamkeleyo iindaba ezimnandi, njengoko atshoyo noIsaya ukuthi: “Nkosi, ngubani na othe wakholwa ludaba lwethu?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ngoko ke ukholo luvuswa ngokuvakaliswa kodaba; ke lona udaba luvakalisa uKrestu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ngaba awevanga na kodwa amaSirayeli? Ewe, avile. Kaloku iziBhalo zithi: “Ukuhlokoma kwelizwi labo kuvakala kuwo wonke umhlaba; namazwi abo afikelela eziphelweni zehlabathi.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ngaba kodwa wona amaSirayeli ayengaqondi? Ukuphendula mandiqale ngoMosis othi: “Mna ndiya kunenza nikhweletele uhlanga olungento; ndiya kunixhokonxa ngohlanga olungenangqondo.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ade atsho nokutsho uIsaya ukuthi: “Ndifunyenwe ngâbo babengandifuni, ndabonakala kwâbo babengabuzisi ngam.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kanti ngokubhekiselele kumaSirayeli uthi: “Imini yonke bendicengana nabantu abangevayo, abandiphikisayo.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngaba uThixo ubalahlile na abantu bakhe amaSirayeli? Nakanye! Nam ngokwam ndingumSirayeli, ndiyinzala ka-Abraham, ndingowendlu kaBhenjamin.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> UThixo akabalahlanga abantu bakhe awabanyula mhlamnene. Kaloku niyayazi *eziBhalweni indawo apho uEliya awamangalela khona kuThixo amaSirayeli, esithi:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Nkosi, amaSirayeli ababulele *abashumayeli bakho, namaqonga akho amadini awadilizile. Ndim ndodwa oseleyo, kwaye nam afuna ukundibulala.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Limphendula njani ke ilizwi likaThixo? Lithi: “Ndizishiyele amadoda angamawaka asixhenxe angamnqulanga *uBhali.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kanti nangoku ke kukwanjalo. Lisekho iqaqobana elichongwe nguThixo ngokwesisa sakhe.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Lona lachongwa nguThixo ngokwesisa sakhe, elibabala, engalinyuli ngenxa yezenzo zalo. Kaloku ukuba uThixo wayenyula abantu ngokwezenzo zabo, isisa sakhe asingebi saba sisisa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kúthiweni ke ngoko? Makuthiwe amaSirayeli akayifumananga into awayeyizondelele. Kodwa iqaqobana elichongwe nguThixo layifumana, aza ke wona amanye aqaqadekiswa,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> njengoko iziBhalo zitshoyo ukuthi: “UThixo ubenze badengeka, baza àbabona ngamehlo, àbeva ngeendlebe; ibe ke unangoku basenjalo.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UDavide naye uthi: “Mababanjwe, bavingcelwe kumatheko abo; mabakhubeke, beve impindezelo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mabamfanyekiswe, bangaboni, babandezeleke maxa onke.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngaba isiwo samaSirayeli sawazisela intshabalalo? Nakanye! Kwathi ngesi siwo sawo usindiso lwazifikela iintlanga, khon' ukuze ziwavusele ikhwele.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Esi siphoso samaSirayeli saluphathela intaphane yeentsikelelo uluntu; ngoko ke ukoyisakala kwawo kwaba yinzuzo enkulu ezintlangeni. Zobeka phi na ke ukusikeleleka iintlanga akuba amaSirayeli ezinikele ngokupheleleyo kuThixo!",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngoku mandithethe nani, zintlanga. Okunene ekubeni mna ndingulowo *uthunywe kuzo iintlanga, ndizimisele ukuwenza ubalasele umsebenzi wam,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ndide ndivusele amawethu ikhwele, ndiyisindise inxalenye yawo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kaloku xa ukulahlwa kwawo kuxolelanise ihlabathi noThixo, koba njani ukwamkelwa kwawo? Kofana novuko lwabafileyo!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ukuba isonka sokuqala sentlama singcwalisiwe ngokwenziwa umnikelo, kwangokunjalo zingcwele zonke ezinye ezenziwe ngaloo ntlama. Ukuba iingcambu zomthi zingcwele, kwangokunjalo namasebe angcwele.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Inxalenye yamasebe omnquma yaqhuzulwa kwamiliselwa amasebe omnquma wasendle esiqwini sawo. Nina ke, zintlanga, ningaloo masebe omnquma wasendle. Nanikwa inxaxheba kwincindi yeengcambu eziphilileyo zomnquma.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Musa ke ukuziphakamisa kunamanye amasebe. Kakade ke wena ungaqhayisa ngantoni? Asinguwe kaloku othwele iingcambu, ziingcambu ezithwele wena!",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kodwa wena uya kuthi: “Aqhuzulwa amasebe, ukuze kumiliselwe mna.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Unyanisile, aqhuzulwa ngenxa yokuba engakholwa, ke wena umi apho umiliselwe khona ngenxa yokuba ukholwa. Musa ke ukuba nekratshi, koko yoyika.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Engawasindisanga nje kaloku uThixo amasebe omthi endalo, angákusindisa njani wena?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Khawukhangele ke ububele nobungqongqo bukaThixo! Okunene úngqongqo kwabo bonayo, kodwa kuwe únobubele, ukuba ùthe wahlala kobu bubele. Kodwa kungenjalo wogawulwa nawe ngokwakho!",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Nawo ke amaSirayeli, ukuba ayahlukana nalo eli phike lawo lokungakholwa, omiliselwa kwakhona. Kaloku uThixo unako ukubuya awamilisele.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Nina zintlanga nikhiwe kumnquma wasendle, naza nathi ngokunxamnye nemvelo namiliselwa kumnquma otyaliweyo. NgamaSirayeli kaloku amasebe omnquma otyaliweyo. Ngenxa yaloo nto ke kulula kuThixo ukuwamilisela kwakuloo mnquma.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mawethu, andithandi ukuba ningayazi le mfihlakalo, hleze nizicingele ukuba niziingqondi, le yokuba inxalenye yamaSirayeli yoqaqadeka lide inani elizeleyo leentlanga liphelele.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kwakuba kunjalo ke xa ewonke uSirayeli uya kusindiswa, njengoko zitshoyo *iziBhalo ukuthi: “Uya kuvela *eZiyon uMsindisi, akuphelise kwindlu kaYakobi ukungahloneli-Thixo;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> nguwo lo ke umnqophiso wam nabo, mhla ndothi ndizicime izono zabo.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ngokuzichasa iindaba ezimnandi amaSirayeli aziintshaba zikaThixo, nto leyo inincedayo ke nina zintlanga. Kodwa ke ngokonyulo lukaThixo aziintanda zakhe ngenxa *yamanyange.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kaloku uThixo akalujiki ubizo lwakhe, engazisoli nangezibabalo zakhe.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Nina ke zintlanga benifudula ningamthobeli uThixo, kodwa ngoku nenzelwe inceba ngenxa yokungamthobeli kwamaSirayeli.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kwangokunjalo namaSirayeli akamthobeli ngoku uThixo, ngenxa yenceba eniyenzelweyo nina, ukuze kamva enzelwe inceba nawo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kaloku uThixo wabaquka bonke abantu ekungamthobelini, ukuze abenzele inceba xa bebonke.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hayi ke bethu ubukhulu bobuhandiba bukaThixo, nobunzulu bobulumko nokwazi kwakhe! Asikuko nokuba aziphengululeki izigqibo zakhe, azilandeki iindlela zakhe!",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kanene: “Ngubani na owakha wayazi ingqiqo yeNkosi, ingubani na owakha waba ngumcebisi wayo?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ngubani khona owakha wayiboleka nto, waza wabuyekezwa ngayo?”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kaloku zonke izinto ziphuma kuyo iNkosi, zikho ngayo, zikholo yona. Mayidunyiswe ke iNkosi kude kube ngunaphakade! *Amen."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ndiyanikhuthaza ngoko, mawethu, ngenxa yenceba kaThixo, ukuba nizinikele nina ziqu nibe lidini eliphilayo, elingcwele, elikholekileyo kuThixo. Leyo ke yindlela yenu efanelekileyo yokukhonza uThixo ngengqiqo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Musani ke ukuthatha isimilo sabantu beli phakade, kodwa iingqondo zenu maziguquke zihlaziyeke, nize niyivume intando kaThixo, yona ilungileyo, ikholekileyo, igqibeleleyo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngalo ubabalo endababalwa ngalo ndithi kuni nonke: Musani ukuzicingela ngaphezu koko umntu amelwe kukuzicingela ngako. Ndaweni yaloo nto yibani neengcinga ezithobekileyo. Elowo nalowo makazikhuthaze ngokokholo aluphiwe nguThixo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku, kwanjengokuba sinamalungu amaninzi mzimbeni mnye, abe ke onke amalungu la engenamsebenzi mnye,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ngokunjalo thina aba, sibaninzi nje, simzimba mnye ngokumanywa noKrestu. Sonke ke ngabanye singamalungu omnye elomnye.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Masizisebenzise ke iziphiwo ezahlukeneyo esababalwa ngazo nguThixo. Ukuba sinesiphiwo sokuvakalisa ilizwi elivela kuThixo, masilivakalise ngokokholo esinalo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ukuba sinesiphiwo sokukhonza abanye, masizingise ekukhonzeni. Ukuba sinesiphiwo sokufundisa, masifundise kangangoko sinako.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ukuba sinesiphiwo sokukhuthaza, masiqine ekukhuthazeni. Ongumabi makazabe izipho ngesisa. Owongameleyo makongamele ngenzondelelo. Owenza inceba makayenze echwayitile.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Uthando malungabi naluhanahaniso. Yithiyeni inkohlakalo; bambelelani kokulungileyo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Thandanani ngokwabazalanayo. Shiyiselanani ngokwenzelana imbeko.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Zondelelani ningatyhafi. Yibani nefuthe loMoya. Yikhonzeni iNkosi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Vuyani, ninethemba nje, ninyamezele ezimbandezelweni zenu, nithandaze ningayeki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ziboneleleni iintswelo zamakholwa, nizikhathaze ngokubuka iindwendwe.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Basikeleleni abanitshutshisayo; sikelelani, ningaqalekisi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Vuyani nabavuyayo, nilile nabalilayo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Yibani moya mnye. Musani ukusukela amawonga; yaneliswani kukuzithoba. Musani ukuzicingela ukuba niziingqondi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Musani ukubuyekeza ububi ngobubi. Zimiseleni ukwenza okulungileyo phambi kwabantu bonke.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Yenzani unako-nako ukuhlalisana ngoxolo nabantu bonke.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Zihlobo, musani ukuziphindezela ngokwenu. Impindezelo yiyekeleni ingqumbo kaThixo, njengoko *iziBhalo zitshoyo ukuthi: “Impindezelo yeyam, kuya kubuyekeza mna, itsho iNkosi.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kaloku iziBhalo zikwatsho nokuthi: “Ukuba utshaba lwakho lulambile, luphe into etyiwayo; ukuba lunxaniwe, luphe into eselwayo; kuba ngokwenjenjalo ke, woba uluvisa udano, khon' ukuze luguquke.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Musa ukoyiswa bububi; boyise ububi ngokulungisa."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Wonke umntu makathobele abasemagunyeni, kuba akukho gunya lingaveli kuThixo. Amagunya akhoyo amiselwe nguThixo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ngoko ke, ochasene namagunya uphikisa ummiselo kaThixo; yaye ke wonke umntu owenza loo nto uzibizela ukugwetywa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kaloku abaphathi aba aboyikeki kubantu abalungisayo, boyikeka kwabonayo. Ukuba ufuna ukungamoyiki osemagunyeni, yenza okulungileyo, yaye ke uya kukuncoma.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku abasemagunyeni zizicaka zikaThixo, khon' ukuze kulungelwe kwawena. Kodwa, ukuba uthe wenza into embi yoyika, kuba abasemagunyeni banikwe igunya lokohlwaya. Kaloku bazizicaka zikaThixo; bayaphindezela, bamohlwaye lowo wonayo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngoko ke bathobeleni abasemagunyeni, ingengakuba nisoyika isohlwayo kuphela, kodwa nangenxa yokuhlonela uThixo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nirhafa nje kaloku, kungenxa yokuba abasemagunyeni bangamagosa kaThixo, ngakumbi xa besenza umsebenzi wabo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngoko ke bonke banikeni okubafaneleyo – irhafu kofanelwe yirhafu, umrhumo kofanelwe ngumrhumo, ukuhlonitshwa kofanelwe kukuhlonitshwa, imbeko kofanelwe yimbeko.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Musani ukuba natyala lanto mntwini, lingelilo elokuthandana. Kaloku omthandayo omnye uwuthobele ngokupheleleyo umthetho.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Imiyalelo ethi: “Uze ungakrexezi, uze ungabulali, uze ungebi, uze ungangqini buxoki, uze unganqweneli,” nokuba nguwuphi umyalelo ongomnye, ushwankathelwa ngelithi: “Uze umthande ummelwane wakho kanye ngale ndlela uzithanda ngayo nawe.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Olu thando ke alunakuze lone mntu. Ngoko ke ukuthanda kukuwuthobela ngokupheleleyo umthetho.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Masenjenjalo ke, sisazi nje ukuba eli selilixesha lokuba sivuke ebuthongweni. Kaloku usindiso lukufuphi kuthi ngoku kunasekuqaleni kwethu ukukholwa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ubusuku buhambile, sekuza kusa. Masahlukane ke ngoko nemisebenzi yobumnyama, sixhobe ngezikrweqe zokukhanya.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Masiziphathe ngokundileka njengabahamba emini, singabi sezindywaleni nasekunxileni, ekuhenyuzeni nasekurheletyeni, singabi namona nazinkani.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> INkosi uYesu Krestu mayibe sisikrweqe senu, ningasilungiseleli isimo senu esonakeleyo ukuze nanelise iinkanuko zaso."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Lowo ke uswele amandla elukholweni, mamkeleni, kodwa kungabi nganjongo yakuphikisana nezimvo zakhe.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Omnye ukholo lwakhe lumvumela ukuba atye nakuphi na ukutya, kodwa yena okholo lubuthathaka utya imifuno kuphela.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Lowo utya konke makangamdeli ozila ukutya okuthile, nalowo uzila ukutya okuthile makangamgwebi otya konke, kuba uThixo umamkele.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Yini na wena ukuba usigwebe isicaka somnye? Kaloku siya kugwetywa yinkosi yaso. Kanti notyayo akayi konakalelwa nto, kuba iNkosi inako ukumgcina.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Omnye okunene uthi umhla othile ubalulekile kunomnye umhla, wumbi ke uthi imihla iyafana. Elowo ke makaqiniseke kweyakhe ingqiqo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Lowo ke ugcina umhla othile, uwugcinela iNkosi. Lowo utya nakuphi na ukutya, esitya nje, uzinikela eNkosini, kuba ubulela uThixo. Nalowo ungatyi konke ukutya, engatyi nje, uzinikela eNkosini, kuba naye ubulela uThixo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Akukho namnye kuthi uziphilelayo, kananjalo akukho namnye uzifelayo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kaloku nokuba sidla ubomi, siphilela iNkosi, nokuba siyafa, sifela iNkosi. Ngoko ke nokuba sidla ubomi, nokuba siyafa, singabeNkosi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kuba kaloku uKrestu wafa, wabuya wadla ubomi, ngenjongo yokuba abe yiNkosi yabafileyo nabaphilayo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wena ke, yini ukuba umgwebe uwenu? Ke wena, yini na ukuba umdele uwenu? Kaloku sonke siya kuma enkundleni kaThixo,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> kuba *iziBhalo zithi: “Ndingophilayo nje, itsho iNkosi, aya kugoba kum onke amadolo, zimdumise uThixo zonke iilwimi.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngoko ke sonke ngabanye siya kunika ingxelo phambi koThixo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Masingabi sagwebana ke – ndaweni yaloo nto masizimisele ukungenzi nanye into enokumkhubekisa imwise esonweni umwethu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ndimanywe neNkosi uYesu nje, ndazi ngokuqinisekileyo ukuba akukho nanye into engàtyiwayo ngokunokwayo. Kodwa kulowo uthi into ayityiwa, ayityiwa ke.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ukuba uyamhlungisa umwenu ngento osukuba uyitya, inkqubo yakho ayiseyiyo eyothando. Musa ukuthi ngenxa yokutya okutyayo umtshabalalise lowo uKrestu wamfelayo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Inkululeko eninayo ekuzikhetheleni ukutya mayingabangi kungcikivana.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kaloku ukukholisa uThixo akungakutya nakusela; kodwa kukwenza ubulungisa, sinoxolo novuyo, silawulwa nguMoya oyiNgcwele.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Owenjenjalo ke ukhonza uKrestu, ukholekile kuThixo, waye usulungekile emehlweni abantu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ngoku ke masizondelele izinto zoxolo nezokwakhana.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Musa ukuthi ngenxa yokutya uwuchithe umsebenzi kaThixo. Okunene konke ukutya kunyulu, kodwa kuba yinto embi kulowo uthi ngenxa yokutya abe sisikhubekiso komnye.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kulungile ukuba ungatyi nyama, ungaseli tywala, ungenzi nantoni na engámkhubekisayo umwenu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Unaluvo luthile na ngale ndawo yokutya? Hlala unalo ke phambi koThixo! Uyavuya lowo ungenasazela ngento ayityayo!",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kodwa ke lowo uthandabuzayo xa atyayo, selegwetyiwe, kuba akatyi ekholwa. Yonke ke into ayenzayo umntu engaqinisekanga ukuba iyamkholisa uThixo isisono."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Thina ke sinokholo olomeleleyo simelwe kukuthwalisana ubunzima nabo balukholo lubuthathaka. Masingazikholisi thina ziqu,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> koko masithi sonke ngabanye sikholise abamelwane bethu ezintweni ezilungileyo ezinokulukhulisa ukholo lwabo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kaloku naye uKrestu akazikholisanga, njengoko nazo *iziBhalo zitshoyo ukuthi: “Izingcikivo zabakungcikivayo zathwalwa ndim.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku zonke izinto eziseziBhalweni zabhalelwa ukusifundisa, khon' ukuze sihlale sihleli sinethemba ngonyamezelo nenkuthazo esizifumana kuzo iziBhalo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Wanga ke uThixo, osinika unyamezelo nenkuthazo, anganenza nibe moya mnye ngokwentando kaKrestu Yesu,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ukuze nithi, ngamxhelo mnye, nimdumise ngazwi-nye uThixo, uYise weNkosi uYesu Krestu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Yamkelanani ke, njengokuba naye uKrestu wasamkelayo, ukuze adunyiswe uThixo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ke kaloku ndithi, uKrestu waba ngumkhonzi wamaJuda, ukubonisa ukuba uThixo unyanisekile, uyazizalisekisa izithembiso awazenzayo *kumanyange.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngokunjalo uKrestu wayenza le nto ukuze neentlanga zimdumise uThixo ngenxa yenceba yakhe, njengoko *iziBhalo zitshoyo ukuthi: “Ngenxa yoko ndiya kukudumisa phakathi kweentlanga, ndiliculele indumiso igama lakho.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kananjalo zithi: “Yibani nemihlali ndawonye nabantu bakhe, nina zintlanga.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kananjalo: “Yidumiseni iNkosi, nonke nina zintlanga; yibongeni, nonke nina zizwe.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kananjalo noIsaya uthi: “Liya kubakho iHlumelo likaJese. Uya kuvela oya kulawula iintlanga. Ziya kuthembela kuye izizwe.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Wanga ke uThixo, umthombo wethemba, angáthi ngokukholwa kwenu anivuyise kakhulu, aniphe uxolo, ukuze ithemba lenu liye lisanda ngokwanda ngamandla oMoya oyiNgcwele.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Mawethu, ndiqinisekile ukuba ningabantu abalungileyo, abanolwazi olunzulu, abanako nokucebisana.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kodwa ke, mawethu, kwezinye iindawo ndinibhalele ndithetha ngokuphandle, ndinikhumbuza kwakhona ngeendawo ezithile. Ndithethe ngokuphandle ngenxa yobabalo uThixo awandibabala ngalo,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ubabalo ke lokuba ngumkhonzi kaKrestu Yesu olungiselela iintlanga. Ngokushumayela iindaba ezimnandi zikaThixo ndisebenza okombingeleli, ukuze iintlanga zibe nokuba lidini elamkelekileyo kuThixo, lingcwaliswe nguMoya oyiNgcwele.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ekubeni ndimkhonza ngolu hlobo uThixo, ndimanywe noKrestu Yesu, ndifanele ukuba neqhayiya.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ke mna andinabuganga bakuthetha nto ngazinto angazisebenzanga ngam uKrestu. UKrestu wasebenza ngam ukuze iintlanga zimlulamele, esebenza ngamazwi am nangezenzo zam,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> esebenza ngamandla emiqondiso nemimangaliso, nangamandla oMoya. Ndithe ke ndaqala eJerusalem, ndajikeleza ndaya kutsho nakwelaseIliriko, ndizivakalisa kuyo yonke indawo iindaba ezimnandi zikaKrestu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ndihlala ndizimisele ukushumayela iindaba ezimnandi apho kungekaviwa nto khona ngoKrestu, ukuze ndingakhi phezu kwesiseko somnye,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> kodwa kube njengoko *iziBhalo zitshoyo ukuthi: “Abo bangaxelelwanga nto ngaye, baya kubona; nabo bengevanga nto, baya kuqonda.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ngenxa yoko bendisoloko ndixakekile, andabi nako ukunihambela.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ngoku ke, ekubeni ndingasenandawo emandiyihambele kule mimandla, nasekubeni ndineminyaka emininzi ndilangazelela ukunihambela,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ndothi ke xa ndihambela eSpeyini, ndinityelele nani, kuba ndinethemba lokunibona xa ndigqitha apho. Emva kokuba ke sendikhe ndaba lundwendwe phakathi kwenu okwexeshana, ndinethemba lokuba nondixhasa ukuya eSpeyini.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kodwa okwangoku ndisaya eJerusalem, ukuya kulungiselela abantu bakaThixo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kaloku kwakholeka kwabaseMakedoni nabaseAkaya ukuba babancede abantu bakaThixo baseJerusalem abasweleyo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Benjenjalo kuba babemelwe kakade kukwenjenjalo. Kaloku ekubeni amakholwa angamaJuda ethe anikela ngezinto ezizezoMoya kwiintlanga, kufanelekile ukuba namakholwa aziintlanga anikele kumaJuda ngezinto zokuxhasa ubomi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ndakuba ke ndiwugqibile lo msebenzi, ndiyinikele kuwo loo mali, ndothi xa ndiya eSpeyini, ndinityelele.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Xa ndinityelelayo ke, ndiqinisekile ukuba ndoniphathela zonke iintsikelelo asisikelela ngazo uKrestu.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ke kaloku, mawethu, ndiyanibongoza ngenxa yeNkosi yethu uYesu Krestu nangenxa yokusithanda kwakhe uMoya, ukuba nindithandazele kuThixo, njengokuba nam ndizithandazela.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ndithandazela ukuba ndihlangulwe kwabangamphulaphuliyo uThixo abakwelakwaJuda. Ndithandazela nokuba kwamkeleke ukubalungiselela kwam abantu bakaThixo abaseJerusalem,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> khon' ukuze ndinihambele ngovuyo ngemvume kaThixo, sichwayitisane.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ke kaloku uThixo, imbangi yoxolo, makabe nani nonke. *Amen."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku ndimyaleza kuni udade uFibhi, oligosakazi kwibandla eliseKenkreya.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mamkeleni egameni leNkosi njengokuba nifanele ukwenjenjalo ningabantu bakaThixo nje. Mncedeni emicimbini asukuba efuna uncedo lwenu kuyo, kuba naye ngokwakhe wanceda abantu abaninzi, endingomnye wabo nam lo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Imibuliso kuPriska noAkwila, abasebenzela uKrestu Yesu njengam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku bona bâbubeka esichengeni ubomi babo ngenxa yam, nto leyo ke ekungabuleli mna ndedwa kubo ngayo, koko kubulela nawo onke amabandla asezintlangeni.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Libuliseni kwanebandla elihlanganela endlwini yabo. Ndibuliseleni kuEpeneto, umhlobo wam othandekayo, owaba ngowokuqala ukukholwa kuKrestu eAsiya;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> nindibulisele nakuMariya owabulaleka kakhulu ngenxa yenu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Imibuliso kuAndroniko noJuniya, amawethu awayebanjwe kunye nam. Bona baxatyisiwe kakhulu *ngabathunywa bakaKrestu, kwaye bâkholwa kuKrestu ngaphambi kwam.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ndibuliseleni kuAmpliyato, umhlobo wam othandekayo eNkosini.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Imibuliso ku-Urbhano, osebenzela uKrestu kunye nam, nakuStaki, umhlobo wam othandekayo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ndibuliseleni nakuApele ovavanyiweyo waza wafumaneka ethembekile kuKrestu. Imibuliso kwabakwa-Aristobhulo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ndibuliseleni kuHerodiyo umwethu. Imibuliso kwabakwaNarkiso abakholwayo eNkosini.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Imibuliso kuTrifena noTrifosa abayisebenzele kangaka iNkosi. Ndibuliseleni kuPersi othandekayo, obulaleke gqitha emsebenzini weNkosi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Imibuliso kuRufo umnyulwa weNkosi, nakunina, onjengomama kum.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Imibuliso kuAsinkrito, uFilego, uHerma, uPatrobha, uHerme, namawethu akunye nabo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Imibuliso kuFilologo noJuliya, uNere nodade wabo, no-Olimpa, nabo bonke abantu bakaThixo abakunye nabo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bulisanani ngokwamakholwa. Ayanibulisa onke amabandla kaKrestu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ke kaloku, mawethu, ndiyaniyala: balumkeleni abaxabanisayo nabakhubekisayo, besenza okuchaseneyo nemfundiso enayifundiswayo nina. Zikhwebuleni kubo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Abantu abanjalo àbakhonzi yona iNkosi yethu uYesu Krestu. Hayi, basebenzela izisu zabo. Ngamazwi abo amnandi bayakhohlisa, balukuhle iintliziyo zabantu abanyulu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bonke bavile ngokumlulamela kwenu uKrestu; into ke leyo endivuyisayo ngani. Ndinga ke ningaba zizilumko okunene kokulungileyo; kodwa ningabi zizo kokubi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ke uThixo, imbangi yoxolo, uya kumnyhasha kamsinya uSathana phantsi kweenyawo zenu. Ubabalo lweNkosi yethu uYesu Krestu malube nani.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Uyanibulisa uTimoti osebenza nam, noLukiyo, noJason, noSosipatro, amawethu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nam Tertiyo osandla siyibhalileyo le ncwadi, ndiyanibulisa ndingoweNkosi nje.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Uyanibulisa uGayo endilundwendwe lwakhe, yena lihlanganela endlwini yakhe lonke ibandla. Uyanibulisa uErasto unondyebo wedolophu, noKwarto umwethu. [",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ubabalo lweNkosi yethu uYesu Krestu malube nani nonke. *Amen.]",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Masimdumise uThixo, yena onako ukunizinzisa elukholweni ngokweendaba ezimnandi endizivakalisayo, ndishumayela uYesu Krestu. Ezi ndaba zityhila imfihlakalo eyayikade ifihliwe mandulo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngoku ke ibonakalisiwe. Yile mfihlakalo ke yayixelwa zizibhalo *zabashumayeli. Babesenjenjalo ngokuyalelwa nguThixo ohlala ehleli. Lo myalelo uThixo uwenze ukuze kubekho abakholiweyo nabamthobelayo kuzo zonke iintlanga.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ke uThixo uSobulumko makadunyiswe kude kube ngunaphakade ngenxa kaYesu Krestu. *Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;